```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8888/houses/search \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "page": 1,
    "pageSize": 6
  }'
```

### Test 2: Text search only
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8888/houses/search \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "query": "luxury",
    "page": 1,
    "pageSize": 6
  }'
```

